### Задание 5.5 — Функция: прибыль за указанный год

```sql
DELIMITER //

CREATE FUNCTION get_profit_by_year(p_year INT)
RETURNS DECIMAL(10,2)
DETERMINISTIC
READS SQL DATA
BEGIN
    DECLARE total DECIMAL(10,2);
    
    SELECT SUM(b.price * od.quantity)
    INTO total
    FROM order_details od
    JOIN books b ON od.idBook = b.idBook
    JOIN orders o ON od.idOrder = o.idOrder
    WHERE YEAR(o.orderDate) = p_year;
    
    RETURN total;
END //

DELIMITER ;
```

Проверь:
```sql
SELECT get_profit_by_year(2023);
```

